  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.10">
<l>cemmoḻivāy nālvēta vāṇar vāḻun tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ ceṅkaṇ mālai</l>
<l>poymmoḻiyoṉ ṟillāta meymmai yāḷaṉ pulamaṅkaik kulavēntaṉ pulamai yārnta</l>
<l>vammoḻivāyk kalikaṉṟi yiṉpap pāṭal pāṭuvārvi yaṉulakil namaṉār pāṭi</l>
<l>vemmoḻikēṭ ṭañcātē meymmai collil viṇṇavarkku viruntākum peruntak kōrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those in this vast world who sing the songs of delight of Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l rend="indent">the clan ruler of the land of Maṅkai, an honest man</l>
<l rend="indent">without any false words,</l>
<l>On whose lips are lovely words full of wisdom about bright-eyed Māl</l>
<l rend="indent">of the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwell nobles on whose lips are the fine words of the four Vedas,</l>
<l>If [they] speak the truth, without fearing hearing the harsh words</l>
<l rend="indent">that Death’s henchmen utter,</l>
<l>Those extremely worthy people will become guests of the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
